snippet.title: Seasons of the Samurai - Trailer
snippet.description:
No guns. No bad guys. No blood. It’s just you against the machine. 

Seasons of the Samurai is a series of puzzles set in medieval Japan that challenges you to use your brain in new and unexpected ways.
